OL,3,CWhen is the deadline to register to
OL,4,Cvote in the General Election?
OL,6,FIn Wales, you can register to vote at
OL,7,Fthe age of fourteen, however in order
OL,8,Fto vote in a General Election, you
OL,9,Fmust be 18 years old or over.
OL,11,FYou must also meet the following
OL,12,Frequirements:
OL,14,FDo I need anything when I vote?
OL,16,FAll voters intending to cast a ballot
OL,17,Fwill not only need to be registered
OL,18,Fbut also show a form of photo
OL,19,Fidentification at the polling station.
