OL,3,CWhen is the deadline to register to
OL,4,Cvote in the General Election?
OL,6,FNearly half a million applications to
OL,7,Fvote were submitted in the past week,
OL,8,Fthe highest number for any seven-day
OL,9,Fperiod so far this year, as the
OL,10,Fdeadline nears for people to register
OL,11,Fto cast a ballot in the General
OL,12,FElection.
OL,14,FA total of 491,144 applications were
OL,15,Fmade in the week to 10 June,
OL,16,FGovernment figures show.
